<normalised orig="vpon" auto="true">upon</normalised> Priests &amp; people? <lb/>
sure I am, <choice ana="print-error">
                     <sic>thosetwelue</sic>
                     <corr>those <normalised orig="twelue" auto="true">twelve</normalised></corr>
